review: It's been almost 2 months and seroquel and CBT is saving my life, marriage and my ability to parent clearly

After many combos of medications used to control my IED (intermittent explosive disorder) within a few months of taking Seroquel, my rages stopped. This is an amazing and very effective medication. I'm only on Seroquel versus the 4 meds I was on prior
Seroquel stopped my explosive disorder like a light switch being turned off. Excellent medicine
